This paper deals with privacy-preserving collaborative clustering, which involves both cryptography and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.DB (Databases), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
